If using ARDUINO IDE, make sure of the following:
1. Navigate to: File>Preferences>Additional boards manager URLs
    Enter the link: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/espressif/arduino-esp32/gh-pages/package_esp32_index.json
2. In the main drop-down (teal tab) select the board: DOIT ESP32 DEVKIT V1
3. Library manager, on the left vertical tab, search: "PubSubClient" by Nick O'Leary. 
    Install.
4. Restart
5. Change SSID and PASSWORD environment variables as needed, lines 9, 10.
